{"tid":397582,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[Live] 其實我唔識做, 會唔會太厹??","createTime":"2017-09-12T14:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T02:01:05.000Z","uid":146588,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab0b1cae3e3be8f01f23da78a71fc518225fa858","tid":397582,"uid":146588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:52:37.000Z","msg":"話說小弟頭先9點到約左三四個朋友黎屋企玩,<br />\n咁之後另外有個女仔遲少少先黎到(唔算太熟),<br />\n正當頭先小弟睇住朋友打機個陣個女仔就黎到,<br />\n咁始終因為人地係我屋企, <br />\n咁正常都應該要問一問人地有咩需要,<br />\n咁我都有問佢要唔要飲下野食下野, 有咩想玩咁...<br />\n<br />\n但如是者真係發生左一個我諗都諗唔到既一幕<br />\n佢既然有少少微笑咁走近我少少講「我想今晚同你一齊訓」...<br />\n咁其他朋友當然聽到亦都有少少起哄,<br />\n但尤於小弟係毒撚, 唔係好識回應,<br />\n到呢家都同個女仔冇兩句講好老尷<br />\n<br />\n真係唔係FF, 其他朋友11點半開始就會走人,<br />\n小弟應該點做好?<br />\n<br />\n利申: 我估其他同佢係有少少曖昧, 但係我估咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03cfb403b202d37226fd915b096fa8f33f46fe4","tid":397582,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:54:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47290497e319296346abb9f3641e8670212adc5e","tid":397582,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:54:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都仲有面扮毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有女嚟屋企玩仲算係咩毒撚"},{"pid":"1f25738ad00b598a2bc3f19e7aeca06e5bb783e8","tid":397582,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:55:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"266bea6f43f8befdb0f1fb590bf4f074b206c0b2","tid":397582,"uid":146588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:55:19.000Z","msg":"ps: 我係唔知佢係認真定講笑, 搞到我唔識點面對佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c242b1f2d5b9ca4e5de9bcec2fe738d6dc20ffd","tid":397582,"uid":146588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T14:56:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都仲有面扮毒撚<img src=\"/assets/fa